# Cloudflare Pages _redirects file for SPA routing

# 重要：优先级从上到下，特定的路由应该放在通用路由之前
# Important: Priority is top to bottom, specific routes should be before generic ones

# 将 /priv/xxx/note 路径重定向到 index.html，保持 URL 不变，状态码 200
# Redirect /priv/xxx/note paths to index.html, preserving the URL, status code 200
/priv/*/note    /index.html   200

# 将 /priv/xxx 路径重定向到 index.html，保持 URL 不变，状态码 200
# Redirect /priv/xxx paths to index.html, preserving the URL, status code 200
/priv/*         /index.html   200

# 将所有其他路径重定向到 index.html，保持 URL 不变，状态码 200
# Redirect all other paths to index.html, preserving the URL, status code 200
/*              /index.html   200
